title: PV exports rise by 2.68 lakh units in last 4 years; Maruti accounts for 70 pc of incremental shipments
description: Passenger vehicle exports from India increased by 2.68 lakh units in the last four fiscal years, with Maruti Suzuki India contributing to nearly 70% of the growth.
